{"tid":809216,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐約市芭蕾舞團男舞者被控散佈女舞者私密照","createTime":"2018-09-07T03:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T03:52:36.000Z","uid":178730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"64de0c477a93ec40470baced201485b5f8c2c4ad","tid":809216,"uid":178730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T03:50:46.000Z","msg":"紐約市一名19歲女芭蕾舞蹈員，對紐約市芭蕾舞團（New York City Ballet，下稱NYCB）和其中一名男舞者提告，指控男舞者在她不知情的狀況下拍攝其私密照，並與其他舞團男性成員交流分享，而舞團對此視而不見。被告男舞者上周無預警辭職，兩名相關男舞者被停職，舞團則否認包庇。<br />\n<br />\n女舞蹈員Alexandra Waterbury與NYCB男舞蹈員Chase Finlay約會一年，Waterbury指控男方私自拍攝兩人的親密照和影片，發送給男同事，用以交換其他女性私密照，還有人主動向Finlay索取。去年9月開始，Finlay<span style=\"font-size: large;\">透過電子郵件散佈一系列女舞者們的裸照和影片</span>，舞團工作人員還向Finlay分享觀賞心得。Waterbury控訴NYCB佯裝不知情，放任性變態為所欲為。<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180907&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58654321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180907%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58654321&d=GWE3d9Tn9k6wFOfB12cPS%2FjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=4668e7e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180907%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58654321&h=a5e5cfa2\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180907&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58654321</a>"},{"pid":"a7ee78194e80e8232dcb901fcbb6c1fc95102f7c","tid":809216,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T03:52:36.000Z","msg":"又網上瘋傳&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}